{
  "id": "5ff43a6e45f7340021fe3e44",
  "title": "最小限の横幅のサイドメニュー",
  "created": 1609841474,
  "updated": 1609843216,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ff43a6e45f7340021fe3e44",
      "text": "最小限の横幅のサイドメニュー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609841474,
      "updated": 1609841474
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43b64aff09e0000b9a36d",
      "text": "コンテンツの横に最小限の横幅のサイドメニューを作りたい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609841509,
      "updated": 1609842146
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43d80aff09e000027ac9f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609842048,
      "updated": 1609842048
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43b85aff09e0000b9a36e",
      "text": "\t[Flexbox]を使う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609841542,
      "updated": 1609842055
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43df1aff09e0000b9a372",
      "text": "\tメニューに幅を指定しなければ中身のサイズギリギリになる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609842162,
      "updated": 1609842162
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43df1aff09e0000b9a373",
      "text": "\t\tデフォルトでflex-basis: autoであることによる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609842162,
      "updated": 1609842174
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43d86aff09e000027aca0",
      "text": "\tコンテンツ側にflex-growを指定。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609842055,
      "updated": 1609842141
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43db5aff09e000027aca2",
      "text": "\t\tデフォルトは0",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609842101,
      "updated": 1609842123
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43dcbaff09e0000b9a371",
      "text": "\t\tこれで「メニューは伸びず、コンテンツだけ伸びる」になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609842124,
      "updated": 1609842154
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43bf1aff09e0000b9a370",
      "text": "\tそれだとメニュー側がピッチリしすぎてて嫌だったのでpaddingを指定した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609841650,
      "updated": 1609842204
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43e1caff09e0000b9a374",
      "text": "\tflexbox以前の古い知識でwidth: 20%とかつけてしまったが、必要なかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609842204,
      "updated": 1609842270
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43b57aff09e0000b9a36b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/8c5966540dd1747f2214e5982110dbec]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609841495,
      "updated": 1609841496
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43b57aff09e0000b9a36c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d87b96100f2a6047f40b6ff699c58877]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609841496,
      "updated": 1609841950
    },
    {
      "id": "5ff43b4faff09e0000b9a36a",
      "text": "code:html",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1609841488,
      "updated": 1609841930
    },
